	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span new=\"\" times=\"\">3.2&nbsp;<font face=\"宋体\">根据用户要求，生产单位可提供钼含量大于或等于</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">54%</font><font face=\"宋体\">和钼含量小于</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">45%</font><font face=\"宋体\">的钼精矿，其杂质含量由供需双方协议。</font></span><span new=\"\" times=\"\"><br />
