<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜二＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">拟定计划</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:
0pt\">根据营<span style=\"color:black\">销科</span>传送的信息拟定配送计划，发出配送通知。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜三＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">做好送货准备</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span style=\"font-size:
14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">准备所需车辆，明确送货目的地。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜四＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">配货</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">集货：配货员将各个用户所需要的各种物品，按需要的品种、规格、数量，从仓库的各个货位拣选并集中起来；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">分拣：分拣员将集货形成的集中物品按运输车辆分开，分别堆放到指定的装卸点；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">配装：配货员将各个用户所需的各种物品、和车辆的装载容量组配起来。装卸工将客户所需的各种货物，以就近原则，按配送车辆的装载容量进行装载组配。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜五＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">送货</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">接营<span style=\"color:black\">销科</span>送货通知单，做送货准备；确认货物种类和数量；需要车辆的大小和数量；运送目的地；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">查看出库单和送货费用缴费单，装货；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">送至目的地。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:
0pt\">二、操作办法<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\"> </span></span></span></b></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜一＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">合同及票据管理</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">合同签订：《运输合同》（见附件一）必须在货物装车前签订；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">票据管理：严格程序、一票多联、核对无误、签字确认，具体见《货物托运单》（附件二）。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜二＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">装卸货管理</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">安全搬运，合理放置；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">装货、卸货及启封开箱时须双方验证。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜三＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆管理</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆有配送部统一管理，由专职司机负责驾驶；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆的各种证件必须齐全；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">货运车辆必须定期或及时检修；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">严禁货运车辆超限、超载。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-font-kerning:0pt\">＜四＞</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">运输货物管理</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">选择最佳运输路线，未经许可禁止改道；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">对非全密封车厢要做好防雨、冰、雪等措施；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;
color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">运输期间未经托运方同意禁止开启封条。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination:widow-orphan\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:
