<p class=\"NewNewNewNewNew\" style=\"line-height:200%\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体\">目的：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:
宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:#0400\">规范</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:
宋体;color:black;mso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:#0400\">业务流程及操作。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体\">适用范围：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN\">本办法适用于</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">业务</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;mso-ansi-language:ZH-CN\">的管理与操作。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">职责：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">仓储金融科负责《</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">业务流程及操作规范》的制定和修改，并对实施情况进行监督。仓储金融科主管领导对</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;
mso-bidi-language:#0400\">前置现货通</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">业务流程及操作规范进行总体控制，仓储金融科具体执行本办法。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">＜一＞业务流程</span></b></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">客户和拟购货物经四方<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>银行、贸易公司、担保公司、仓储公司<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>认可；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">客户与贸易公司签订《委托采购协议》；贸易公司与供货方签订《购销合同</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">》，客户在银行存入其购货物一定比例的采购资金；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
16.0pt;font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>3.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">客户存入采购资金后，根据《委托采购协议》和《购销合同》，就货款资金缺口部分提</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">交借款申请；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">贸易公司按照贷款金额的<span lang=\"EN-US\">50%</span>在银行存入过程保证金，此款项由银行予以冻结；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">经银行审批后，与客户签订手续，担保公司提供担保；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">银行放款至客户账户，并先于冻结；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">7.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">客户与贸易公司确定提货日期后，共同签署《用款申请》，经银行审核后，先将款项转入贸易公司专用账号，由贸易公司按《购销合同》转入供货方账号；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">8.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">客户、贸易公司、担保公司共同提货、检验，直至货物到达仓储公司仓库；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">9.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">开具仓单，由贸易公司将仓单通过背书方式，将货物交付客户；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">10.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">客户将货物质押给银行，变成现货通；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">11.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">偿还贷款，银行发放解除质押通知书，提货；</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0\">
	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
color:black\">12.</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;color:black\">程序结束。</span></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">＜二＞操作办法</span></b></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;
layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:
14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">按照</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">《前置现货通实施细则》操作</span></b></p>
<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.1pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;
layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:none\">
	<b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:16.0pt;font-family:宋体\">附件：</span></b><a href=\"http://www.mushw.com/uploads/前置现货通.doc\">前置现货通.doc</a></p>
