ze: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: \"yes\"; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">千瓦时，水的重复利用率大于</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: \"arial\"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: \"yes\"; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">80%</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: \"宋体\"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: \"yes\"; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: \"宋体\"; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: \"yes\"; mso-shading: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
