	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">温度对钼硬度的影响示于图</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">9</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">，不管是室温或高温，钼的硬度值都能大致转换成抗拉强度，这种关系见图</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">10</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
