\'; \">℃由包晶反应生成，它没有多晶型转变。当钼的浓度在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">65-70</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">％</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">重量</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">)</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">范围内，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Mo</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; vertical-align:sub; \">2</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Zr</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">的晶格常数有变化，这就表明这个相有均相区。含</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Mo68</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">％</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">重量</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">)</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">的合金在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1350</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃退火</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New 