<p>
	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">3</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">）</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">铪</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">：</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Hf</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Mo</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">中的溶解度随着温度的下降而减少，温度由</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1960</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃降到</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1200</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃时，溶解度由</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">35</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">％降到</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">9.5</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">％。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Mo-Hf</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">系统的状态图见图</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">29</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">。化合物</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">MoHf</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Iaves</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">相，该相是在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1960</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃发生的包晶反应产物，它的均相区很窄，有两个多晶型转变。在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">900</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">-</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1800</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃之间，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">MgCu</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; vertical-align:sub; \">2</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">型面心立方晶格的同素异构体相是稳定的。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
