imes New Roman\'; \">Cr</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; vertical-align:sub; \">2</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Zr</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">为基的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">&mdash;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">固溶体，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Zr</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">基</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">&nbsp;&beta;&mdash;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">固溶体，锆在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Mo</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">和</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Cr</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">中的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">&nbsp;&alpha;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">固溶体。</span></p>
