\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">HfC</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">在钼中的溶解度分别为</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">3.3%</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">和</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">0.5%(</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">重量</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">)</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">。当提高合金中</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Ti</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">Zr,Hf</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">的含量时，起初碳的溶解度增高，而后下降。在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">2100</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1800</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1500</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">℃和</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1200</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10