<p>
	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">4&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">典型的钼合金化合物</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p>
	&nbsp;</p>
<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:125%; \">
	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">4.1&nbsp;TZM</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">合金</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:125%; \">
	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">4.1.1&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">合金成分与性能</span></p>
<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:125%; \">
	<span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;工业生产中最早的钼合金为钛锆钼合金，它是在</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Mo-0.5Ti</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">（</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Mo-0.5Ti-0.01</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">～</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.04C</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 31.5pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">）合金的基础上通过加入锆而形成的。在难熔金属合金中以强度高、良好的导热导电性及膨胀系数低、再结晶温度高，同时又比较容易加工而著名。</span></p>
<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:125%; \">
	<span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;TZM</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">合金的成分是：钛</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.4</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％～</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.55</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％，锆</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.06</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％～</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.08</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％，碳</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.01</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％～</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">0.04</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％，余量为钼，合金元素总量不超过</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">％。加入锆不仅使合金进一步强化和提高再结晶温度，而且扩大了碳在钼中的溶解度，并使合金具有热处理敏感作用。此合金的组织结构，通常是在钼的</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&alpha;</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">固溶体的基体上明显分布有块状</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Mo-C</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">和少量弥散的</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">TiC</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ZrC</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">。这些少量的元素，使钼的力学性能不论是室温还是高温都大为提高，再结晶温度比纯钼高</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">300</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">℃左右，与钨相比，钨的强度虽然要比钼合金高一些，但由于钨的密度</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">19.3g/cm</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; vertical-align: super;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">是</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">TZM</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">钼合金（</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">10.2g/cm</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; vertical-align: super;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">）的</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">1.87</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">倍，因此</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">TZM</span><span style=\"line-height: 125%; text-indent: 26.25pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">合金的强度比纯钨高。</span></p>
<p class=\"p0\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; line-height:125%; \">
	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">TZM</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">合金的生产方法有熔炼法及粉末冶金法两种。采用粉末冶金法可以节省真空自耗电弧炉、大型挤压机和锻锤以及相应的高温加热炉等大型设备，使工序简化，生产周期缩短，能耗降低，生产能力及成品率成倍提高，因此成本大大降低。表</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">2</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">2</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">为这两种生产方法生产的钼合金板材的性能比较。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:center; line-height:125%; \">
