	<span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;TZM</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">钼合金热变形加工比较困难，尤其圆棒，若不经过热挤压变形而直接锻造，合金的成品率则相当低。因此烧结后的合金锭，首先应进行热挤压开坯，然后再锻造。如果能合理地控制好加热温度及热挤压和锻打时的变形量，便可以使</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">TZM</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">合金的力学性能达到理想状态。由于</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">TZM</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">合金是属于脆性材料，锻打时易产生裂纹，在锻造时必须采用大变形量并快速锻打，否则锻坏的可能性较大。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
